arlink):** 122\n\n*Source: Footnote (1) in the Preamble section.*\n\n### **Average Revenue per Customer Launch in FY2025**\nUsing the revenue and customer launch figures from FY2025:\n*   **Total Space Segment Revenue:** $4,086 million\n*   **Customer Launches:** 43\n\n**Estimated Average Revenue per Customer Launch:** ≈ **$95 million** ($4,086 million / 43 launches).\n\n**Important Context:** This average is a simplification. Actual revenue per launch varies significantly based on the contract type (e.g., a single commercial launch vs. a multi-year government development contract). The company notes that while total Falcon launches increased, "Launch Services missions" (customer launches) remained relatively flat, and "average price per launch remained relatively flat year over year."',
